OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777395954
OL,3,CA mother's journey after losing child
OL,4,Cto cancer to turn dreams to memories
OL,6,FWatching a child die, regardless of
OL,7,Ftheir age, is one of the most
OL,8,Ftraumatic and soul-wrenching
OL,9,Fexperiences for a parent.
OL,11,FFor Geraldine Magill, she looked after
OL,12,Fher daughter, Lisa, as she battled a
OL,13,Frare cancer. Lisa's spirit and courage
OL,14,Fwas unmatched.
OL,16,FShe even penned a blog 'Terminally
OL,17,FFabulous' to chronicle her journey and
OL,18,Fhelp others going through a similar
OL,19,Fordeal.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
