PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777395954
OL,3,CA mother's journey after losing child
OL,4,Cto cancer to turn dreams to memories
OL,6,FA few months before Lisa passed away,
OL,7,Fthe family who were then living in
OL,8,FAustralia, was approached by a charity
OL,9,Fwho offered to bring them on holiday.
OL,11,FThis was something Geraldine says they
OL,12,Fcouldn't have even thought possible
OL,13,Fbut the charity with its expertise
OL,14,Forganised everything and within days
OL,15,Fthe family were on a trip which would
OL,16,Fbuild memories forever.
OL,18,FAs Lisa said, for once during years of
OL,19,Fstruggles, they felt like a normal
OL,20,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777395954
OL,3,CA mother's journey after losing child
OL,4,Cto cancer to turn dreams to memories
OL,6,FGeraldine said: "Within five days, we
OL,7,Fwere on that, that aeroplane, and can
OL,8,FI just say, from the second we stepped
OL,9,Fon it, it was nearly like we had left
OL,10,Feverything cancer back in Brisbane.
OL,12,F"I know that sounds so far fetched,
OL,13,Fbut that's exactly how we felt as a
OL,14,Ffamily, we actually, in Lisa's own
OL,15,Fwords, we felt like a normal family
OL,16,Fand we hadn't done that for a very
OL,17,Flong time."
OL,19,FLisa died in March 2017. She was only
OL,20,F35 years old.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777395954
OL,3,CA mother's journey after losing child
OL,4,Cto cancer to turn dreams to memories
OL,6,FHaving returned back to Northern
OL,7,FIreland, Geraldine knew that she
OL,8,Fwanted to give back and she truly
OL,9,Funderstood the gift which had been
OL,10,Fgiven to them with that final trip.
OL,12,FAnd from that desire to pay it back,
OL,13,Fcame Geraline's charity
OL,14,F'Dreams2Memories.'
OL,16,FDreams2Memories was set in March 2025
OL,17,Fand since then it has helped over 25
OL,18,Fpeople with life-limiting conditions
OL,19,Fto fulfil their wishes.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777395954
OL,3,CA mother's journey after losing child
OL,4,Cto cancer to turn dreams to memories
OL,6,FFrom family photoshoots to meet and
OL,7,Fgreets with Westlife, Gerladine has
OL,8,Fworked tirelessly not just to keep the
OL,9,Fcharity going but to keep it funded so
OL,10,Fit can continue to help the most
OL,11,Fvulnerable.
OL,13,F"We have never had to decline a dream,
OL,14,Fwhich is massive to me and my
OL,15,Fdetermination to make sure that stays
OL,16,Fis 100%," said Geraldine.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777395954
OL,3,CA mother's journey after losing child
OL,4,Cto cancer to turn dreams to memories
OL,6,FWhen I ask Geraldine about how easy it
OL,7,Fis to get funding and donations, she
OL,8,Fis as astute as she's determined. She
OL,9,Fpoints out that there is barely a
OL,10,Ffamily which hasn't been touched by
OL,11,Fcancer in some form. But also, there
OL,12,Fare pressures on our health system.
OL,14,FFor Geraldine, she knows her charity
OL,15,Fcan offer something different.
OL,17,FDreams2Memories can give patients and
OL,18,Ftheir families something positive to
OL,19,Flook forward to.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777395954
OL,3,CA mother's journey after losing child
OL,4,Cto cancer to turn dreams to memories
OL,6,FAs Geraldine says herself, cancer
OL,7,Foften reduces families to caregivers
OL,8,Fbut when you get a break, when you
OL,9,Fspend an afternoon together - even if
OL,10,Fonly for an hour, you are a family
OL,11,Fagain.
OL,13,F"For the dreamer themselves, it's just
OL,14,Fhaving something to look forward to
OL,15,F... just that, right, on Sunday we're
OL,16,Fgoing to be doing this," said
OL,17,FGeraldine.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777395954
OL,3,CA mother's journey after losing child
OL,4,Cto cancer to turn dreams to memories
OL,6,F"It's something to plan and look
OL,7,Fforward to, and it's actually
OL,8,Fsomething that you don't have to do
OL,9,Fyourself, which lifts a lot of weight.
OL,11,F"The thing for the family is, and it
OL,12,Fwas the same for us, you see an
OL,13,Fimmediate change in the cancer
OL,14,Fsufferer.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777395954
OL,3,CA mother's journey after losing child
OL,4,Cto cancer to turn dreams to memories
OL,6,F"Look, there's not a lot to look
OL,7,Fforward to when you have a diagnosis
OL,8,Flike that, and for the family to see
OL,9,Fthat their mother, their daughter,
OL,10,Ftheir sister, their brother, whoever
OL,11,Fit is, is going to have something that
OL,12,Fthey really want, it kind of lifts the
OL,13,Fwhole family."
OL,15,FWebsite: Dreams2memories
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
OL,20,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,21,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
